<p>The open sided, palm roofed main rancho is the center of Esperanza life. Spacious and airy, it has a large hammock lounge, communal dining area and plenty of space for doing your own thing. If you can tear yourself away from the beach we have a library with a great selection of hundreds of books, in English, Spanish, and other languages, as well as a large selection of board games, two guitars, and a drum.</p>

