<p>You have the choice of two dormitories each sleeping six, seven private bamboo caba&ntilde;as sleeping up to four, and spacious grounds providing shaded camp sites for your tent or hammock.</p>

<p>You&rsquo;ll get a great night&rsquo;s sleep on our comfortable mattresses in our bamboo caba&ntilde;as that let the sea breeze in!</p>

<p>Two of our caba&ntilde;as have spacious private showers and toilets (made from recycled glass bottles), and we have another caba&ntilde;a with a private toilet. All of our caba&ntilde;as have personal palm-covered hammock areas where you can relax in your own space.</p>

